## The Referral Flywheel

```
Client Success
     ↓
Ask for Testimonial
     ↓
Client Shares (naturally or asked)
     ↓
New Leads Discover You
     ↓
Some Convert to Clients
     ↓
[Repeat with each new client]
```

### Accelerating the Flywheel

| Acceleration Tactic | Implementation |
|--------------------|----------------|
| **Referral bonus** | "Get 1 month free for each referral who signs" |
| **Co-branded content** | Client's post about working with you |
| **Sneezer gifts** | Thoughtful gift after referral converts |
| **Case study sharing** | Tag client when sharing their story |

